{"author":{"id":"df79d9acb56ef89cd944cc8548377a5d54d09f0704d032bd86e5f202c0cd02f7"},"ops":[{"type":3,"timestamp":1493826135,"nonce":"yqROqOMy0gdXW16k7R5KP8S1PkM=","metadata":{"github-id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDI5ODk1MDM5Nw==","github-url":"https://github.com/galaxyproject/tools-iuc/issues/522#issuecomment-298950397"},"message":"As @bgruening explained on https://github.com/bioconda/bioconda-recipes/pull/4590 while these specific examples might not have been able to get the older Biopython conda packages from the bioconda channel, they were available in the default anaconda channel.\n\nPresumably if there are any missing conda dependencies, they will be restricted to those not under automated testing, i.e. https://github.com/galaxyproject/tools-iuc/blob/master/.tt_blacklist","files":null},{"type":3,"timestamp":1494348052,"nonce":"Lyc/6Y9zkCsTPPkx0jsYn0QGUjs=","metadata":{"github-id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDMwMDIyNTYxOQ==","github-url":"https://github.com/galaxyproject/tools-iuc/issues/522#issuecomment-300225619"},"message":"I've realised the hard way that the automated testing of tools from this repository does not necessarily cover all the IUC packages, e.g.\n\n* https://toolshed.g2.bx.psu.edu/view/iuc/package_ghostscript_9_07/ (and https://toolshed.g2.bx.psu.edu/view/devteam/package_ghostscript_9_10 too) were missing in BioConda, fixed in https://github.com/bioconda/bioconda-recipes/pull/4650\n\n* https://toolshed.g2.bx.psu.edu/view/iuc/package_gnuplot_4_6 was broken in bioconda, hopefully fixed in https://github.com/bioconda/bioconda-recipes/pull/4655\n\nI will likely stumble over more as I gradually work on my tools with a recent version of planemo which does the dependencies via conda. At some point I will likely switch my own tool continuous integration testing away from ``tool_dependencies.xml`` and manual installation to using conda.\n\nBut in general, It would be useful for the community as a whole if all the IUC and devteam packages could be cross-referenced against BioConda (and the other recommended Conda channels) to confirm if a matching version is available.","files":null}]}